{"tid":2083673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"惡法殺到 海外升學查詢飆五成","createTime":"2020-06-29T02:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T02:21:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"da66849a7ff29edc6b26ebbd3818198d257577ae","tid":2083673,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:10:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200629/QPNVQOY477HOEB42W6DSXVZWZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200629%2FQPNVQOY477HOEB42W6DSXVZWZA%2F&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8SPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=f81c3ef0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200629%2FQPNVQOY477HOEB42W6DSXVZWZA%2F&h=242a9029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200629/QPNVQOY477HOEB42W6DSXVZWZA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n惡法殺到 海外升學查詢飆五成<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】極權之手隨國安法伸進我城尋常百姓家，全港人人自危。作為下一代移民途徑之一的海外升學，需求激增。在昨日一個升學展覽上，有家長明言惡法殺到令他們對香港前途感到悲哀，現時正加緊準備子女的海外升學計劃。升學機構表示，今年查詢海外升學詳情的人數較去年大增30至50%，相信升幅與近期時局有關。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YWQmeG4YL5KCeaYQJgA7Imy26C0=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DXUADF7WP4CTNQHKQWZJZCOEM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYWQmeG4YL5KCeaYQJgA7Imy26C0%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDXUADF7WP4CTNQHKQWZJZCOEM4.jpg&h=33ec60e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n升學博覽會昨吸引不少家長及學生到場了解海外升學資料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n家長：無謂要子女留港受苦<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：跟蹤13日 四神秘人監視黎宅<br />\n<br />\n昨日在九龍灣國際展貿中心舉行的《明報》高中生升學博覽會2020，人頭湧湧。記者現場所見，海外升學機構攤位的詢問人數，較本地大學及自資院校攤位為多。家長大多查詢英、美、澳、加等港人移民熱門國家的升學指南。<br />\n<br />\n海外升學機構「ASTON Education」助理經理黎芷筠表示，今年查詢海外升學的人數較去年增加30至50%，認為升幅確實<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n青睞。<br />\n<br />\n偕同女兒到場的石太稱，本來打算先讓女兒在香港讀至中學畢業後才計劃讓她到海外升學，但港版國安法迫使她<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n審查，「當你一舉一動俾人監控住，其實都幾恐怖」。<br />\n<br />\n另一家長李太亦表示，當前局勢亦令她對香港失去信心，希望「小朋友走得就走」。<br />\n。。。。。。"},{"pid":"1c1061982dd89769188bd82a4bb5790145ab1896","tid":2083673,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9HE0Php.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9HE0Php.jpg&h=c5e5f272&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"560954354e7117d6317200afaa894905109b0a3f","tid":2083673,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:11:43.000Z","msg":"走就有用架喇咩"},{"pid":"429b3984e381993136a3fff38c4b7b7334e7fcfd","tid":2083673,"uid":78411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"71見"},{"pid":"e3a1c809e83ea8a974ed5331b5a51d1f3dc88484","tid":2083673,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:12:33.000Z","msg":"藍絲子女有冇返中國讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b18dc95f95e7a9b062455b4eb09292a16ed8ed","tid":2083673,"uid":206466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:13:01.000Z","msg":"又做逃兵！？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n曲"},{"pid":"42d8fa301b1e00e708bd739a6e74b151213c3732","tid":2083673,"uid":106408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"藍絲要走就返蚛蟈"},{"pid":"ffa4335a653e298b5acf693a4ac753eefbcba2f5","tid":2083673,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"429b3984e381993136a3fff38c4b7b7334e7fcfd","tid":2083673,"uid":78411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"71見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:20:04.000Z","msg":"71見"},{"pid":"86b522c934d051bd2dde1abf3b4e1570a40661b3","tid":2083673,"uid":345925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:21:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆